metadata.name: Baby Joker - Death Card
metadata.description:
This freaky boy is Baby Joker, he was just a little baby doll, with a kind cute face, that kids loved to play with
His story begins with pain!
when he was trapped in the Magician's Dungeon, struggling to free the poor kid from the Magician's cruel hands, he got cursed by the Magician and lost his big eyes
he was no longer able to see!
but after the 11th week, he found a magical card that was made by the Magician to do evil stuff and murder the kids
He finally killed the Magician with a swing of the card and got away from the dungeon
Death, he named the card
He tried so hard to forget the child, but every night, the city could hear him cry, a weeping sound that doesn't stop when a kid is alone in the park
The Baby Joker just couldn't stop himself from crying, so he sewed his lips
such a hurtful pain he couldn't bare
He's got a dead heart inside his cold body now, which makes him follow you in the darkness
To hunt you down and slice ur sanity with a swing of his card.
...
